HEADWORD: Fleeten
<hw>Fleet"en</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Fleeted or skimmed
milk.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Fleeten face</b></col>, <cd>a face of the color of
